Remember these events are tailored to your group.  Imagine if there is no event that requires a rogue if there is not one in the group... But if one is there.. then it is required.<br>
<br>
Honestly think about what you thought what EQ would be before you ever started playing or had a firm understanding of how it worked?  I imagine it was something like this...<br>
<br>
Get a group of other people together, go into a dungeon and kill all the mobs, overcoming traps and obstacles along the way.  Finally reaching the end of a nearly empty dungeon to take on the Lord of the Lair and defeating him and getting some nice loot.<br>
<br>
